            <p>J. JUDELSOHN&#44;<lb/>					
                EXPERT<lb/>
                AND<lb/>
                Professional Accountant&#44;<lb/>
                <del>248 East Broadway</del>&#44;<lb/>
                123 East 46<hi rend="sup">th</hi> St<lb/></p>
            <p>Books and complicated accounts examined&#44; audited and balanced.<lb/>  
                Balance sheets&#44; Statements and Statistics systematically prepared.<lb/>  
                Partnership accounts examined for arbitration and re&#45;stated for legal<lb/> 
                and other purposes.  Single&#45;entry books proved by Double&#45;entry.<lb/>
                <emph rend="italics">All kinds of temporary or permanent work on books or busi&#45;<lb/>
                    ness documents solicited.  Best city references.</emph><lb/></p>
                
            <p>New York&#44; June 26 1887<lb/></p>
                
            <p>&#91;Hebrew&#93;<lb/></p>
                
            <p>My dear Rabbi S. Morais<lb/></p>
            <p>The above quotation from<lb/> &#34;Pyrpe Abath&#34; can be applied<lb/> to you&#44; may his grace rest<lb/> upon you and your beloved<lb/> family and to our coreligionists<lb/> all over the world.<lb/></p>
            <p>The honor which was con&#45;<lb/>ferred upon you by the<lb/> University of Pennsylvania<lb/> confirms the above quotation<lb/> and hope to see you success&#45;<lb/>full in all your lifetime&#44; this<lb/> is the sincere wish of yours<lb/> very resply J Judelsohn<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
            <p>Mr Henry S Morais<lb/></p>
            <p>My dear Sir&#58;&#45;&#45;I will use<lb/> this <sic>occation</sic> to remind you<lb/> that your beloved and honored<lb/> father has kept up his repution&#91;&#63;&#93;<lb/> up to date and contributed<lb/> with it to the <sic>wellfare</sic> of our<lb/> coreligionists in general.  Therefore<lb/> use the opportunity now to study<lb/> hebrew and the talmud so that<lb/> you may become a worthy<lb/> successor to your father&#45;&#45;<lb/></p>
            <p>Use the good and valuable<lb/> time&#44; <sic>dont</sic> waste it&#45;&#45;and by<lb/> doing so you will have a<lb/> good future for yourself and<lb/> and for our coreligionists<lb/> in <sic>generall</sic> your truly<lb/> J Judelsohn<lb/></p>
            </body>
